---
title: Baja-Style Blackened Prawns with Garlic Rice & Smokey Slaw
description: There’s a hint of smokiness in the air and it’s coming from these prawns! The All-American spice works magic when cooked onto
this fresh seafood and served on top of a bed of rice. Not to mention, the smokey aioli tossed through the slaw. It’s a firestorm of flavour tonight!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

